This elegant glass pearl necklace features a bold 12mm crystal rhinestone center fireball with graduated pearls going fully around the neck. Our adjustable 16" - 18" necklace is available in White or Soft Cream at an incredible wholesale price.  This essential piece of wedding jewelry should be a part of every bridal retailer's display case. Our necklace is handmade in the USA.
productdescription_abovepricing: Mariell's elegant glass pearl bridal necklace has a 12mm crystal rhinestone fireball center & 12mm pearls on either side which gradually taper down to 6mm. This regal bridal neck is adj. 16" - 18" & is offered in Soft Cream or White at a great low price!
